{"tid":1636424,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[隱藏身份] 多人全黑就係隱藏身份，少人全黑就係焦點","createTime":"2019-10-07T17:51:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T16:11:22.000Z","uid":179379,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0ed9f53131850f48d4bd03a875b2d582207cf671","tid":1636424,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T17:51:08.000Z","msg":"全黑<br />\n係用嚟避搜證<br />\n唔係用嚟避追捕<br />\n<br />\n所以當快閃，或者進場離場時<br />\n人數唔多嘅全黑就會被target<br />\n<br />\n狗可以透過記者live、藍屍報料、卧底去追蹤你嘅位置<br />\n再配合新戰術，揸架車去附近再落車捉人<br />\n導致今日開花傷亡慘重<br />\n所以我哋必須要檢討<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Black Bloc</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n全黑已經好多人做𡁵<br />\n而得個<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">濕鳩口罩</span>，或者<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">顏色背囊</span>嘅，麻煩再改善吓<br />\n仲有你件<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">黑色衫反轉著</span>咪睇唔到logo囉<br />\n<br />\n詳情可以睇我嘅舊Post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1583191/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1583191/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">進場 / 離場</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n避Cam換衫之前講過，自己睇返上面條Link<br />\n呢度主要講<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">心態</span>，特別係如果你有<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">文具</span>喺身<br />\n<br />\n你著街坊裝就係街坊，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">唔需要戴口罩</span>，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">唔需要驚狗</span>亦<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">唔好仇視犬隻</span>，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">唔好討論夢境</span><br />\n同時<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">留意哨兵Channel</span>，選擇安全路線<br />\n而當<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">大量狗隻搜捕</span>，可以喺<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">安全地方等耐啲</span>，千祈唔好強行進場 / 離場<br />\n<br />\n撚狗嘅責任交返畀真街坊<br />\n而你嘅責任只有<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">安全去到現場同返屋企</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">快閃</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n快閃最緊要就係<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>快</strong></span></span>，做完就走，唔好停留<br />\n移動速度亦要快，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">唔好慢慢散步</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">人數唔可以多<br />\n目標亦都唔可以多</span><br />\n<br />\n完成目標數量就<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">即時散水</span>，唔好貪心<br />\n最好就係做完都冇人知<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>題外話：撚狗</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n言語對狗隻其實傷害唔大<br />\n同埋依家鳩咬街坊<br />\n所以街坊撚狗一定要<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">保持適當距離</span><br />\n知自己<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">跑得慢</span>嘅，就自己<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">行遠少少</span><br />\n<br />\n圍住嘅街坊最緊要係不被捕<br />\n實際傷害等高位手足嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">記住，行動派少一個就少一個<br />\n大家務必小心</span>"},{"pid":"c1a168e1354c78aa59adcc120bb9d7f8880df35d","tid":1636424,"uid":121387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T17:53:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"708c3f929b4f6d4c239a9fdc45c61a25cc32ce1c","tid":1636424,"uid":37739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T17:55:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"61f2f7e8ed1c851063ceb1c04c7407393d9c062a","tid":1636424,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T17:56:38.000Z","msg":"大家心態一定要升級<br />\n出到嚟就唔好掛住吹水散步<br />\n<br />\n出面有好多職業揀<br />\n快啲嗱嗱聲轉返個職"},{"pid":"4a0ce210d3862b680f4fa9ea96c329a85ce6d1ab","tid":1636424,"uid":255313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T17:57:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"03d7c69c9a88ea09a57793c89ca0cb765843eeec","tid":1636424,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T17:57:59.000Z","msg":"【facebook戰線】大家一齊report曬D垃圾page，等佢地重蹈點新聞嘅覆轍<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eewfbS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eewfbS</a><br />\n<br />\n【地方的手足需要進化】麻煩大家入黎溫下書，睇下烏克蘭係E個時候做左D咩<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejgzzS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejgzzS</a>"},{"pid":"b74ce944057ac4f8e851306150eb5312ef6e66f8","tid":1636424,"uid":130140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T17:58:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1eba631c35d2e3ea3df83ecb8adfbafa0d140919","tid":1636424,"uid":27894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T18:00:30.000Z","msg":"Agger<br />\n任何行動，保護自身同附近嘅人嘅安全係最緊要<br />\n齊上齊落、出入平安係要靠每一位嘅謹慎"},{"pid":"459cda6404f0906d8de19bf825d3a48f6a00307d","tid":1636424,"uid":179379,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T18:00:50.000Z","msg":"仲有，真係要做嘢嘅，麻煩你包好啲個樣<br />\nCap帽、面巾、手套係必須<br />\n<br />\n如果你得個濕鳩口罩<br />\n我唔介意你做返和理非<br />\n因為一百部閘機，都唔及我哋一個手足咁珍貴"},{"pid":"301835bb94fb396db431fd1e67696c951480054f","tid":1636424,"uid":295304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T18:02:31.000Z","msg":"P但推"},{"pid":"55302e1adb5176ad5750359c7e5c3a43ac145368","tid":1636424,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T18:03:39.000Z","msg":"同埋大家要量力而為<br />\n跑得慢就係跑得慢﹐唔夠力就唔夠力<br />\n無論你有幾想幫手都係改變唔到呢個事實<br />\n<br />\n認清自己嘅能力<br />\n揀返適合自己嘅位置"},{"pid":"06cf82e770e6e92e142fc0b16cfbd9cb4f0e418f","tid":1636424,"uid":77872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T18:14:02.000Z","msg":"推撚到你仆街"},{"pid":"688c2dbd0e690394c492b69f80171c2aa878de0a","tid":1636424,"uid":156064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T18:17:44.000Z","msg":"和勇相連"},{"pid":"c1be4d993b3d50df7bd782224f7e0d6dc107eb61","tid":1636424,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T19:31:26.000Z","msg":"自己推"},{"pid":"ef8d236d61b3239e5ca783902364b75b88a4869e","tid":1636424,"uid":186874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T19:32:28.000Z","msg":"be watee<br />\n（幫推上熱門）可唔可以推返啲正經野<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1636594\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1636594</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"71934b8e942346ec4fc3e08cba2b310474f66c9b","tid":1636424,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T19:43:14.000Z","msg":"推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8baf106a62167b50b9b510bc4688c1de1486b383","tid":1636424,"uid":76059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T19:46:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a06ed78f2b11434712c885b01070e28950e3f87f","tid":1636424,"uid":174120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T20:43:25.000Z","msg":"策略正確"},{"pid":"a458bfdee3cf8facbe5dbe843ee246a8dc41db54","tid":1636424,"uid":104507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T20:56:47.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"06340c1c1d4f1265cfaa3c503afbf26a2698ef0c","tid":1636424,"uid":287019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:34:12.000Z","msg":"高質 但我推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d51b174510cc0196a3bf1ec192c38e235a7da93","tid":1636424,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:17:16.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"d1d582e7c88d6f8b0ddce2cd5c0929f1de3942e8","tid":1636424,"uid":259639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:11:22.000Z","msg":"「仲有你件黑色衫反轉著咪睇唔到logo囉」<br />\n屌係bo，點解我諗唔到 仲要專登買全黑衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}